Georgiana Young https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Georgiana_Young 0 Georgiana Young Montalban (born Georgiana Paula Belzer; September 10, 1924 – November 29, 2007) was an American actress, the maternal younger half-sister of actresses Loretta Young, Polly Ann Young, and Sally Blane. She had a brief career in film, appearing alongside her sisters in the biographical drama The Story of Alexander Graham Bell (1939), followed by bit parts in two other films.
